Review: New lens on life and could not stop laughing i aspire every day to be bella

I am reminded that Todd Haynes is always and forever my favorite… everything about this is delicious ,, different from his other work but also keeping with his tradition, makes new and interesting use of the trappings of melodrama and his continuous interest in artifice and performance. And it’s really fucking funny
Obsessed with so many choices Jessica Lange made in this. One of her best
I would be just as easily charmed and manipulated by Ann Dowd
